ace!<br><br><br>Play <strong>solo</strong> or with up to <strong>4 friends</strong> in this fun Colony-Building, Automation, Defense adventure<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349040/extras/c794038afe2135244785ab0e667bbb6a.poster.avif?t=1725190932\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349040/extras/c794038afe2135244785ab0e667bbb6a.webm?t=1725190932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349040/extras/c794038afe2135244785ab0e667bbb6a.mp4?t=1725190932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
